name: Shop Direct Brands Inc.
overview: ShopDirectBrands.com offers Industrial supplies, absorbents, material handling, and safety products from top brands like 3M, Brady, Erogdyne, Kimberly Clark and more. We want to provide you with name brand products you know and trust. Sometimes suppliers pick and choose products from a manufacturers portfolio. We try to show the entire product line so that you can make the best possible choice without compromising. Brands you know and trust like 3M, Post-It, Scotch, Rubbermaid, and Kimberly Clark. Other trusted brands like Loctite, Kidde, MSA , WD-40,and Ergodyne just to name a few more.
